author: nurfikri89
body: This PR adds Pileup jet ID BDT training weights for AK4 Puppi (V18) jets, which was produced by Jihoon Shin (@jshin96). The  DYto2L Winter24 JMENanoV14 sample was used for the training. Details of the training were presented in a JMAR [meeting](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1429230/#3-run3-pileup-jet-id-training).
title: AK4 Puppi V18 jets Pileup jet ID BDT training weights
